{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"90394-unkawu-nongwenya","title":"UNkawu noNgwenya","description":"Do the Ape and the Crocodile have a happy friendship story?","language":"isiZulu","langCode":"zu","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Pumla Mdontswa"],"illustrators":["Abraham Muzee"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/90394-unkawu-nongwenya"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130933/size3/94684613766dee09332eba2857f49e9b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130933/size6/94684613766dee09332eba2857f49e9b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128943/size6/9127b41d835a908628913be4a343e9bf.jpg","text":"UNkawu uhlangana\nnoNgwenya ngasechibini.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128944/size6/6a8420f04d7cba8a9f4b6aaad8a6dd7a.jpg","text":"UNkawu ubuza uNgwenya, \"Ngabe uhlalaphi?\" \nAphendule uNgwenya, \"Echibini.\"","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128946/size6/30f582dfb8154af7d8aef6b9622e0b18.jpg","text":"UNgwenya ke naye\nbese ebuza uNkawu.\nAphendule\nuNkawu, \"Ngihlala\nezihlahleni.\"","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128948/size6/0ba1353f30edfb15718a0843f424adc9.jpg","text":"Aqhubeke uNgwenya,\n\"Uyakwazi \nukubhukuda?\"","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128949/size6/7e5bf5576f54e0edaab3a9af5b820a29.jpg","text":"\"Cha, angikwazi.\"\nUNgwenya-ke beseethi,\n\"Ngizokufundisa.\"","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128951/size6/fa99f2c1819415f62ae8fd81a30a19a2.jpg","text":"Aqhubeke uNgwenya,\n\"Ungesabi,\nsingabangane.\"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128956/size6/438ffbbb59de882f937e4a56eaaf6398.jpg","text":"Khona laphouNgwenya athi\nkuNkawu,\n\"Umalume wami\nuyagula, udingainyama.\"","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128960/size6/9faac76e7e8232b6e842cd97de25bc0c.jpg","text":"UNkawu\nuseyasaba\nngempela manje.\nNgabe uNgwenya\nuzomudla?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128962/size6/ade52cc5479a0a2de3376d29ada2e13e.jpg","text":"UNkawu ufuna\nukubalekela\nuNgwenya manje.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128964/size6/1d33c83a83af05a90c19120daf14d089.jpg","text":"Hmm! Usenesu.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128965/size6/3025f20b829b9b343274686bbeab94a5.jpg","text":"UNkawu bese\nethembisa\nuNgwenya,\n\"Ngizokunika\ninhliziyo yami,\nuphe umalume\nwakho.\"","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128967/size6/8778e6d6e3f1ce0481cc7f83ee1dcecc.jpg","text":"\"Kodwa-ke,\nmngane wami,\ninhliziyo yami\nisemhlabeni,\nesihlahleni,\"\nkuchaza uNkawu.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128968/size6/2a9c36bbd4a2d51e825ea69a71b399d9.jpg","text":"\"Ungayilanda\ninhliziyo yakho\nlapho?\" kubuza\nuNgwenya.\nAvumele phezulu\nuNkawu, \"Yebo,\nyebo.\"","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128970/size6/199064dbef69a3d993de1d50383effea.jpg","text":"Nanguya\nuNgwenya\nebhukuda eya\nemhlabeni.\nNanguya noNkawu\negijimela\nezihlahleni.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128972/size6/67f2317dd9bd1b8e072fb711a2e89ff6.jpg","text":"UNgwenya\nwezwakala esethi,\n\"Awuyena\numngane wami.\nUqambe amanga!\"","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128974/size6/bc60af238f2e2a589a04c62f2b994439.jpg","text":"Waphendula\nuNkawu\nesihlahleni, \"Vele,\nasibona abangane!\nUcabanga ukuthi\nangiboni ukuthi\nufuna ukungidla\nungishwabadele!\"","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":117}}